# Slice 19/30: the admin dashboard is embedded into ddb-server at compile
# time via include_dir!. We commit a minimal stub index.html so the rust
# crate compiles in fresh checkouts before `npm run build` has run. CI and
# the Dockerfile rebuild the dashboard before cargo, overwriting the stub.
!packages/admin/dist/
!packages/admin/dist/index.html

